The paper deals with the problem of learning local image descriptors using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes the use of global loss functions to improve the generalization capability of the model, which is a topic that falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also evaluates the performance of the proposed methods on a benchmark dataset, which is a topic that falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
